{
  "stem": "214.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And-- and I-- and I think that probably till now-- but they-- they destroyed most of the houses that we were in in Miedzyrzec, in '84.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Especially the ghetto was all gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But I am sure that-- that people were talking about it-- that the walls there were just full of furs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And people were hoping that after the war, they will take them out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Because these were those fur merchants.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how this sort of-- sort of went, you know, that the beginning of 1942.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then this-- and then my sister-- where was she?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, this was later, after the first deportation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my sister and I, we would-- though people sort of used us as-- as communicators.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, I would go several times to the Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was [NON-ENGLISH], another city.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People would have friends there or would have people assumed they left some.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once, I know I brought-- which-- but it was the night of-- of the deportation from Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was this one family who moved to-- to Miedzyrzec.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think Biala was being-- but this was not totally apparently juden-- made judenrein before.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because one of the boy-- one of the sons of this family in Biala Podlaska, he got engaged to one of my cousins.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They never got married either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is he disturbing you?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After he say-- I mean, they never got married.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But his family must have been a pretty-- and he, since he was born then, he probably also, like my cousin, [NON-ENGLISH], he knew all those Poles and probably some of the Germans also.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had a permit to travel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know if he was part of the Judenrat maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
